milestones.description: Andy Flower and Grant Flower's 124-run partnership is ZIM's highest for the 1st wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 79 between Andy Flower and Ali Shah
Dave Houghton and Mark Dekker's 69-run partnership is ZIM's highest for the 3rd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 51 between Dave Houghton and Andy Pycroft
Dave Houghton has broken the record for most sixes (10) in ODIs for ZIM, going past Andy Waller's 8
Eddo Brandes has become the top wicket-taker for ZIM in ODIs with 19 wickets, going past John Traicos's 17
Eddo Brandes has conceded the most runs in an innings (74) in ODIs for ZIM, going past Kevin Duers's record of 72
This is the highest match aggregate (543) involving teams New Zealand & Zimbabwe in ODIs
Dave Houghton has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (23) for ZIM, going past John Traicos
